  "datePublished": "2026-03-01",
  "description": "A shuffle is the process of randomizing the order of cards in a [deck](./deck.md) before setup or between rounds in a [card game](../index.md). Shuffling is what introduces uncertainty into a card game — without it, the card order would be known or predictable, and the game would become a puzzle rather than a contest of strategy under uncertainty.",
